can be distinguished from the other two males known from 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Casal" authorityYear="1962" box="[1293,1436,151,175]" class="Insecta" family="Mutillidae" genus="Horcomutilla" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="576" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
